title: Finishing Grace
itunes:title: Finishing Grace
description:
Philippians 1:6 promises that He Who began a good work in you will continue to perform it until it’s complete. You are destined to finish with a flourishing finish! Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
